   Saint Brother André

Our mission

   Saint Joseph’s Oratory of Mount Royal, founded by Saint Brother André,
   is a Catholic shrine dedicated to Saint Joseph. Place of expression of
   faith, prayer, healing and peace, the Oratory welcomes pilgrims and
   visitors in a spirit of openness and compassion.
     __________________________________________________________________

Our vision

   To be, in the heart of the city, the place of openness, gathering and
   reflection, where the heritage of Saint Brother André thrives.

   Visit the online store

   Discover a wide variety of religious items, devotional objects and
   more.
